---
layout: base.njk
title: Training
description: Sidemount diving courses from recreational intro through full technical trimix, taught by a RAID Tech Trimix Sidemount Instructor.
permalink: /training/
---

<div class="training-page">

  <header class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">RAID-certified instruction</span>
      <h1>Sidemount Training</h1>
      <p>From your first sidemount dive to trimix exploration — every course built around the AXIS Method and the principles that actually matter underwater.All training based out of Florida unless otherwise requested. Contact us to schedule Turk traveling to you </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="training-courses" aria-labelledby="courses-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sr-only" id="courses-heading">Available courses</div>

      <div class="course-list">
        {% for course in collections.courses %}
        <article class="course-card" id="course-{{ course.data.id }}">

          <div class="course-card-image">
            <img
              src="{{ course.data.image }}"
              alt="{{ course.data.image_alt }}"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="course-card-content">
            <span class="eyebrow">RAID</span>
            <h3>{{ course.data.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ course.data.description }}</p>

            <div class="course-meta">
              <div class="course-meta-item">
                <span class="course-meta-label">Duration</span>
                <span class="course-meta-value mono">{{ course.data.duration }}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="course-meta-item">
                <span class="course-meta-label">Investment</span>
                <span class="course-meta-value mono">{{ course.data.price }}</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top:0.5rem;">
              <a href="/contact/?course={{ course.data.id }}" class="btn btn-signal btn-sm">Enquire →</a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band" aria-labelledby="training-cta-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 id="training-cta-heading">Not sure where to start?</h2>
      <p>Every diver is different. Get in touch and we'll work out the right pathway for your experience and goals.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-signal">Get in Touch</a>
        <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-ghost">About the Instructor</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>
